- **`freeman/drizzle/0001_products.sql`** — SQL migration with `CREATE TABLE` + `ALTER TABLE products ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY` + a public SELECT policy (products are the public catalogue; service role bypasses RLS for writes).
- **`freeman/lib/db.ts`** — updated to pass the schema to `drizzle()` for type inference.
- **`freeman/lib/schema/products.test.ts`** — 5 tests covering table name, column presence, nullable `imageUrl`, and default values for `stock` and `isActive`.
