Done. Here's what was shipped in commit `01d4d9b`:

- **`drizzle/0004_carts.sql`** — `carts` and `cart_items` tables with RLS enabled; authenticated users can manage their own rows; guest carts are server-side only (postgres superuser via Drizzle)
- **`lib/schema/carts.ts`** — Drizzle schema + inferred TypeScript types
- **`lib/cart-cookie.ts`** — HMAC-SHA256 signing/verification for guest session IDs using Node's built-in `crypto`; no new dependencies
- **`lib/cart.ts`** — `getOrCreateGuestCart`, `getOrCreateUserCart`, `mergeGuestCartToUser` (quantities summed for items in both carts)
- **`lib/env.ts`** — `CART_SECRET` added as required env var
- All 93 tests green

